verbose_text: Western blotting analysis and ALP activity measurement showed that expression levels of CaSR and of osteogenic markers including collagen I, Runx-2, OCN, and ALP, were significantly upregulated in the Cal group and thereafter inhibited by NPS-2143, an allosteric antagonist of CaSR.
